0.5.name: wordpress/wp-walla
0.5.description:
Gowalla is a "Here am i" service that allows you to check in to various places so your friends can see what you are up to.

WP-Walla allows you to show your gowalla checkin's on your wordpress blog. The plugin is design to work as a sidebar widget or by manually put a code snipper in your template.

WP-Walla caches the data in a file.

You can easily change plugin settings under the WP-Walla option i the settings menu.

More info: Official plugin site
